title: Clinical Application Of Mechanical Ventilation - 4th Edition.pdf
description:
CLINICAL APPLICATION OF MECHANCIAL VENTILATION, FOURTH EDITION integrates fundamental concepts of respiratory physiology with the day-to-day duties of a respiratory care professional. Utilizing the wide degree of topics covered, including airway management, understanding ventilator wave-forms, and addressing critical care issues, readers have the best resource available for understanding mechanical ventilation and its clinical application. Whether preparing for the national exam or double-checking a respiratory care calculation, this book provides the fundamental principles of respiratory care with the clinical guidance necessary for mechanical ventilation.

Publication : January 31, 2013
Format : PDF
Size : 42.7MB
Pages : 768
